<p>If you're not sure how overrides work, read our <a href="http://www.ostraining.com/blog/drupal/drupal-overrides/">introduction to Drupal overrides</a>.</p>
<p>One of the most powerful ways to override Drupal is with sub-themes and sometimes even with sub-sub-themes. These allow you to safely override any themes you download from Drupal.org.</p><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/ostrainingdrupal/~4/OE6Z0xiOjWI" height="1" width="1"/>
